features = pd.get_dummies(df.drop('species', axis=1)).dropna()

    perplexity=30,
    metric="euclidean",
    callbacks=ErrorLogger(),
    n_jobs=8,
    random_state=42,
).fit(features)

def get_species(row):
    for c in ['species_Adelie', 'species_Chinstrap', 'species_Gentoo']:
        if row[c]==1:
            return c
